            "type": "TEXT",
            "data": "Engineering Complete. 41000000 rows ready on RTX 3060.\n+--------------+-----------+--------------+\n|is_high_volume|tx_id_float|total_with_tax|\n+--------------+-----------+--------------+\n|           1.0|     3.69E7|      551.3724|\n|           1.0|     3.69E7|      616.8312|\n|           1.0|     3.69E7|      245.6136|\n|           1.0|3.6900004E7|       408.024|\n|           1.0|3.6900004E7|      767.8368|\n+--------------+-----------+--------------+\nonly showing top 5 rows\n\nimport org.apache.spark.sql.functions._\nimport org.apache.spark.sql.types._\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mgoldPath\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32mString\u001b[0m \u003d /home/thedude/hazynet-lakehouse/gold/retail_sales_final\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mrawDF\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame\u001b[0m \u003d [tx_id: bigint, full_name: string ... 4 more fields]\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mlabelCol\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32mString\u001b[0m \u003d is_high_volume\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mfeatureCols\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32mArray[String]\u001b[0m \u003d Array(tx_id_float, total_with_tax)\n\u001b[1m\u001b[34mengineeredDF\u001b[0m: \u001b[1m\u001b[32morg.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame\u001b[0m \u003d [is_high_volume: double, tx_id_float: float ... 1 more field]\n"
